description: Lists route calculator resources in your Amazon Web Services account.

parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: An optional maximum number of results returned in a single call. Default Value: 100

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: The pagination token specifying which page of results to return in the response. If no token is provided, the default page is the first page. Default Value: null.

nested_items.name: Entries
nested_items.description: Lists the route calculator resources that exist in your Amazon Web Services account.

nested_items.name: Description
nested_items.description: The optional description of the route calculator resource.

nested_items.name: DataSource
nested_items.description: The data provider of traffic and road network data. Indicates one of the available providers:

nested_items.name: CreateTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp when the route calculator resource was created in ISO 8601 format: YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ss.sssZ.

nested_items.name: UpdateTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp when the route calculator resource was last updated in ISO 8601 format: YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ss.sssZ.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: A pagination token indicating there are additional pages available. You can use the token in a subsequent request to fetch the next set of results.
